harvesting.

00:51:30.900 --> 00:51:34.460
You've heard of high dynamic
range, right?

00:51:34.460 --> 00:51:38.510
Or how to make your picture look
like a Harry Potter set?

00:51:38.510 --> 00:51:43.870
This is EXDR, Extending the
Dynamic Range of everything.

00:51:43.870 --> 00:51:46.210
You can extend the dynamic
range of time.

00:51:46.210 --> 00:51:48.520
You can extend the dynamic
range of focus.

00:51:48.520 --> 00:51:50.250
You can extend the dynamic
range of blur.

00:51:50.250 --> 00:51:51.980
You can extend the dynamic
range sharpness.

00:51:51.980 --> 00:51:55.530
You can extend the dynamic range
of color, in addition to

00:51:55.530 --> 00:51:57.485
