range of exposure.

00:52:00.070 --> 00:52:04.540
You have to look at what it is
you want to say, what it is

00:52:04.540 --> 00:52:05.350
that you want to leave.

00:52:05.350 --> 00:52:08.560
What is the best thing
of you if not the

00:52:08.560 --> 00:52:09.700
images you leave behind?

00:52:09.700 --> 00:52:12.310
What is going to outlast you?

00:52:12.310 --> 00:52:14.740
It is the imagery that you leave
behind if you choose

00:52:14.740 --> 00:52:16.560
photography as the
way in which you

00:52:16.560 --> 00:52:18.190
choose to express yourself.

00:52:18.190 --> 00:52:21.600
Because there are many other
ways to express yourself.

